TrenchBroom - TrenchBroom is level editor for Quake-engine based games.

TrenchBroom is a free (GPLv3+), cross platform level editor for 
Quake-engine based games. It supports Quake, Quake 2, and Hexen 2 
and runs on Windows (XP and newer), Mac OS X (10.6 and newer) and 
Linux. TrenchBroom is easy to use and provides many simple and 
advanced tools to create complex and interesting levels with ease.

